{"ts": "2026-06-09T17:03:55.348923+00:00", "update": {"tools": {"messages": [{"type": "tool", "data": {"content": [{"type": "text", "text": "| MCP:BJGLg0 | successfully downloaded text file (SHA: 6e90e2d5b8c4ddca40dea68ada13a608abb2f4f7)", "id": "lc_f723af7a-5aa8-467d-8d10-1afcd28ba14e"}, {"type": "text", "text": "| MCP:BJGLg0 | import logging\n| MCP:BJGLg0 | \n| MCP:BJGLg0 | import sqlalchemy\n| MCP:BJGLg0 | from databases import Database\n| MCP:BJGLg0 | from sqlalchemy.orm import sessionmaker\n| MCP:BJGLg0 | from sqlalchemy_utils import database_exists, create_database\n| MCP:BJGLg0 | \n| MCP:BJGLg0 | from .settings import settings\n| MCP:BJGLg0 | \n| MCP:BJGLg0 | \n| MCP:BJGLg0 | db = Database(settings.DB_URL)\n| MCP:BJGLg0 | metadata = sqlalchemy.MetaData()\n| MCP:BJGLg0 | engine = sqlalchemy.create_engine(settings.DB_URL, pool_size=3, max_overflow=0)\n| MCP:BJGLg0 | if not database_exists(engine.url):\n| MCP:BJGLg0 |     create_database(engine.url)\n| MCP:BJGLg0 | \n| MCP:BJGLg0 | LocalSession = sessionmaker(autocommit=False, autoflush=False, bind=engine)\n| MCP:BJGLg0 | \n| MCP:BJGLg0 | metadata.create_all(engine)\n| MCP:BJGLg0 | \n| MCP:BJGLg0 | \n| MCP:BJGLg0 | def get_db():\n| MCP:BJGLg0 |     \"\"\"\n| MCP:BJGLg0 |     A dependency for working with PostgreSQL\n| MCP:BJGLg0 |     \"\"\"\n| MCP:BJGLg0 |     try:\n| MCP:BJGLg0 |         db = LocalSession()\n| MCP:BJGLg0 |         yield db\n| MCP:BJGLg0 |     except Exception as e:\n| MCP:BJGLg0 |         logging.error(e)\n| MCP:BJGLg0 |     finally:\n| MCP:BJGLg0 |         db.close()", "id": "lc_ac1588d9-e270-4b81-bef0-b8b5d72df4cb"}], "additional_kwargs": {}, "response_metadata": {}, "type": "tool", "name": "get_file_contents", "id": "b1fb5c99-6ff5-44b3-b4df-c2bda1b0f417", "tool_call_id": "call_8eae8ee3d1844cc0b1f4a923", "artifact": null, "status": "success"}}]}}}
{"ts": "2026-06-09T17:04:14.044859+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "This FastAPI template uses the following primary Python dependencies and service stack:\n\n## Core Framework\n- **FastAPI** (with `[all]` extras) – the web framework\n- **Uvicorn** – ASGI server (implied by `main.py` usage)\n\n## Database\n- **PostgreSQL** as the relational database service (via Docker Compose)\n- **psycopg2** – synchronous PostgreSQL driver\n- **asyncpg** – async PostgreSQL driver  \n- **databases** (with `postgresql` extra) – async database abstraction\n- **SQLAlchemy** – ORM and core database toolkit\n- **SQLAlchemy‑utils** – database utility helpers (e.g., `database_exists`, `create_database`)\n- **Alembic** – database migration tool (config in `alembic.ini`)\n\n## Authentication & Security\n- **python‑jose** (with `cryptography` extra) – JWT token encoding/decoding\n- **passlib** (with `bcrypt` extra) – password hashing (`bcrypt` scheme)\n- **python‑multipart** – form data parsing for OAuth2 password flow\n- **FastAPI’s OAuth2PasswordBearer** – integrated OAuth2 token authentication\n\n## Redis Support\n- **aioredis** – async Redis client library\n- **Redis** service (Alpine image) defined in `docker-compose.yml`\n\n## Additional Tools\n- **pytest** – testing framework\n\nThe application runs as a containerized service alongside PostgreSQL and Redis, with environment configuration managed via `.env` files.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 541, "prompt_tokens": 12059, "total_tokens": 12600, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 221, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 11456}}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "mimo-v2.5-pro", "system_fingerprint": null, "id": "603c2ed179054d5ba23e3ee3df81b7cb", "finish_reason": "stop", "logpr